  ?g_33 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#reifies> <<( <http://example.com/ns#a> <http://example.com/ns#b> <http://example.com/ns#c> )>> .
  <http://example.com/ns#s> <http://example.com/ns#p> ?g_33 .
